data.description: Located in the highly sought after Silver Creek subdivision, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has been meticulously maintained. With a formal dining, eat-in kitchen, breakfast bar, and open floor plan hosting family and friends will be no problem. The kitchen boasts matching stainless steel appliances and beautiful granite countertops. Retreat to the oversized primary suite with ensuite bath unlike any other. The dual sinks, garden tub, and walk-in closet allows for plenty of room to get ready for the day. Two guest rooms share a hall bath and the impressive laundry has an abundance of storage! Step outside and hang out on the concrete back porch or by the fire-pit and watch the kids play in the fenced in backyard. This won't last long! Call today to schedule your showing!
